data.description: Great Opportunity to own a 2020 Built - Single Family - 4 Bedrooms - 2 Full Bathrooms - ONE LEVEL with massive space with just under 2000 SQUARE FEET for the type of home.  2 Car Garage and large driveway allows you to park your cars.  Top 10 Features include Upgraded longer cabinets and doors, Keyless Entry, Water softener, Alarm from Guardian and control app, Water irrigation system, recessed lights throughout and All the appliances. Neighborhood with only RESIDENTS no short term rentals allowed which builds community with your neighbors.  Fenced Yard with 5,502 Square foot lots which keeps you from being on top of your neighbor.  Tile Floors throughout, new carpets and move in ready.  Close to schools and bus pickup so they can commute without you.  Low taxes, sellers must sell and you will have a perfect home.  For Quick immediate tour ( milton james dot net ).   This wont last as it is priced under market value.  The solar Panels must be taken over by the buyer which the payments are way less than any electric bill you can ever pay. This one is a no brainer and the best value in the market.  Setup a showing right now before you miss out as we just sold a similar one in 3 days in the same neighborhood.
